<subSubSection id="B787C8CE3DE96A24A24521C586B4D9BD" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" type="notes">
<paragraph id="2C335CAB2C4FEBF7028B3359C80F7970" pageId="0" pageNumber="563">Notes.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="80326BDCBB03FD1BC051EB807A7A494E" pageId="0" pageNumber="563">
<bibRefCitation id="C4A59B1FA789552F9C66883FF2C3F182" DOI="https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1365-3113.1938.tb01241.x" author="Netolitzky, F" journalOrPublisher="Proceedings of the Royal Entomological Society of London - Series B: Taxonomy" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" pagination="37 - 39" refId="B44" refString="Netolitzky, F, 1938. Beitraege zur Kenntnis der Bembidion -Arten des fernen ostens (Japan, Korea, Ostsibirien) (Coleoptera). I. Mitteilung. Proceedings of the Royal Entomological Society of London - Series B: Taxonomy 7: 37 - 39, DOI: https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1365-3113.1938.tb01241.x" title="Beitraege zur Kenntnis der Bembidion - Arten des fernen ostens (Japan, Korea, Ostsibirien) (Coleoptera). I. Mitteilung." url="https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1365-3113.1938.tb01241.x" volume="7" year="1938">Netolitzky (1938)</bibRefCitation>
describes 
<taxonomicName id="ED5151091DE7E7509AD4AA64561DA356" authorityName="Neri &amp; Toledano" authorityYear="2021" baseAuthorityName="Neri &amp; Toledano" baseAuthorityYear="1938" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Bembidion (Peryphus) pseudolucillum" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pseudolucillum" subGenus="Peryphus">Bembidion (Peryphus) pseudolucillum</taxonomicName>
from Settsu (Japan), assigning it to the group of 
<taxonomicName id="3D47CB1F2494A2184473460B7AA18F19" genus="B." lsidName="B. nitidulum" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" rank="species" species="nitidulum">
<emphasis id="2B5F29FC08B7DE63C53EC412E105793E" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="563">B. nitidulum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Marsham, 1802, s. l. (= 
<taxonomicName id="1D435219FFBDD92D6D9202C848329E16" genus="B." lsidName="B. deletum" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" rank="species" species="deletum">
<emphasis id="F7771B92234B700BD9BBF8768BADBE6A" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="563">B. deletum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Serville, 1821); again 
<bibRefCitation id="EA04F2B20F152657406850EA4D81A808" author="Netolitzky, F" journalOrPublisher="Proceedings of the Royal Entomological Society of London - Series B: Taxonomy" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" refId="B45" refString="Netolitzky, F, 1943a. Bestimmungs-Tabellen europaeischer Kaefer (9. Stück). II. Fam. Carabidae. Subfam. Bembidiinae. 66. Gattung: Bembidion Latr. Bestimmungstabelle der Bembidion-Arten des palaearktischen Gebietes. (Mit Hinweisen auf holarktische, aethiopische und orientalische Arten). Koleopterologische Rundschau 28(4/6): 69/41-124/96." title="Bestimmungs-Tabellen europaeischer Kaefer (9. Stu ̈ ck). II. Fam. Carabidae. Subfam. Bembidiinae. 66. Gattung: Bembidion Latr. Bestimmungstabelle der Bembidion-Arten des palaearktischen Gebietes. (Mit Hinweisen auf holarktische, aethiopische und orientalische Arten). Koleopterologische Rundschau 28 (4 / 6): 69 / 41 - 124 / 96." year="1943 a">Netolitzky (1943a</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="867435A781F93CF7A2BC1493A80AFD48" author="Netolitzky, F" journalOrPublisher="Proceedings of the Royal Entomological Society of London - Series B: Taxonomy" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" refId="B46" refString="Netolitzky, F, 1943b. Bestimmungs-Tabellen europaeischer Kaefer (9. Stueck). II. Fam. Carabidae, Subfam. Bembidiinae. 66. Gattung: Bembidion Latr. Bestimmungstabelle der Bembidion-Arten des palaearktischen Gebietes. (Mit Hinweisen auf holarktische, aethiopische und orientalische Arten). Koleopterologische Rundschau 29: 1/97-70/166." title="Bestimmungs-Tabellen europaeischer Kaefer (9. Stueck). II. Fam. Carabidae, Subfam. Bembidiinae. 66. Gattung: Bembidion Latr. Bestimmungstabelle der Bembidion-Arten des palaearktischen Gebietes. (Mit Hinweisen auf holarktische, aethiopische und orientalische Arten). Koleopterologische Rundschau 29: 1 / 97 - 70 / 166." year="1943 b">1943b</bibRefCitation>
) found it difficult to find a correct position for the species in his Bestimmungs-Tabellen: he mentions similarities both with species of two subgenera, 
<taxonomicName id="52A7A388E1181DD72163ECC836AA83A0" genus="Bembidionetolitzya" lsidName="Bembidionetolitzya" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="94B54C7EF65716E8C0BB2943B781E83A" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="563">Bembidionetolitzya</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Strand, 1929 and 
<taxonomicName id="5B2800685EF57560B3861D27B33B6BC8" authorityName="Dejean" authorityYear="1821" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Peryphus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Peryphus" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="CC19150E139C9A39893247FCE956823D" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="563">Peryphus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Dejean, 1821, but preferred the latter. 
<bibRefCitation id="28620638CA96037B20065FB8A306DFA3" author="Jedlicka, A" journalOrPublisher="Entomologisk Tidskrift" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" pagination="202 - 208" refId="B18" refString="Jedlicka, A, 1965. Neue Carabiden aus den Sammlungen des Riksmuseums in Stockholm (Coleoptera - Carabidae). Entomologisk Tidskrift 86: 202 - 208" title="Neue Carabiden aus den Sammlungen des Riksmuseums in Stockholm (Coleoptera - Carabidae)." volume="86" year="1965">
<normalizedToken id="0E725178297A4EC5F7C339164122D397" originalValue="Jedlička">Jedlicka</normalizedToken>
(1965)
</bibRefCitation>
, in his monograph on the 
<taxonomicName id="A7FFCB4042808F4DCC4EC8A056F8F9DC" authorityName="Stephens" authorityYear="1827" lsidName="" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" rank="tribe" tribe="Bembidiini">Bembidiini</taxonomicName>
of Eastern Asia, includes the species in the keys for subgenus 
<taxonomicName id="0AE188A2B24661B5E74FCF93B7F1564A" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Plataphus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Plataphus" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Plataphus</taxonomicName>
Motschulsky, 1864 and that of the subgenus 
<taxonomicName id="BFC477F8FE114BD074E561E3E2BFF8AB" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Plataphus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Plataphus (Peryphus)" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subGenus" subGenus="Peryphus">Plataphus Peryphus</taxonomicName>
. The species is listed in &quot;incertae sedis&quot; in the last catalogues (e.g., 
<bibRefCitation id="BDC94AE04F42D2932AE82A45A1A5D658" author="Marggi, W" journalOrPublisher="Apollo Books, Stenstrup" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" refId="B28" refString="Marggi, W, Huber, C, Mueller-Motzfeld, G, Hartmann, M, 2003. Carabidae: Bembidiini: Bembidiina: 242-273. In: Loebl I, Smetana A (Eds) Catalogue of Palaearctic Coleoptera (Vol. 1). Archostemata - Myxophaga - Adephaga. Apollo Books, Stenstrup" title="Carabidae: Bembidiini: Bembidiina: 242 - 273. In: Loebl I, Smetana A (Eds) Catalogue of Palaearctic Coleoptera (Vol. 1). Archostemata - Myxophaga - Adephaga." year="2003">Marggi et al. 2003</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="F3191DD644666D4899A9A4A95193981B" author="Lorenz, W" journalOrPublisher="Brill, Leiden-Boston" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" refId="B26" refString="Lorenz, W, 2005. Systematic List of Extant Ground Beetles of the World (2nd edn.). Tutzing, 530 pp." title="Systematic List of Extant Ground Beetles of the World (2 nd edn.). Tutzing, 530 pp." year="2005">Lorenz 2005</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="CCD1A185D41FB0E5EEA62FEE4331B02A" author="Marggi, W" journalOrPublisher="Brill, Leiden" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" refId="B29" refString="Marggi, W, Toledano, L, Neri, P, 2017. Carabidae: Bembidiini: Bembidiina: 294-342. In: Loebl I, Loebl D (Eds) Catalogue of Palaearctic Coleoptera (Vol. I). Archostemata - Myxophaga - Adephaga. Brill, Leiden" title="Carabidae: Bembidiini: Bembidiina: 294 - 342. In: Loebl I, Loebl D (Eds) Catalogue of Palaearctic Coleoptera (Vol. I). Archostemata - Myxophaga - Adephaga." year="2017">Marggi et al. 2017</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="608C18A3FFA7DCD10909E6E67E6F4838" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" type="conclusions">
<paragraph id="A1A2CF632439003265C2B7E7587AA63E" pageId="0" pageNumber="563">Conclusions.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="F3045575C04C78D2E88A720F68ADA0D3" pageId="0" pageNumber="563">
The examination of the holotype and of the aedeagus (Fig. 
<figureCitation id="D4EB7DD773AA4518AAB3ED50698CF799" captionStart="Figures 5–9" captionStartId="F2" captionText="Figures 5 - 9. Median lobe of the aedeagi of 5 Bembidion (Peryphanes) sanatum Bates, 1883, holotype (NHMUK), 1.55 mm 6 B. (P.) dostali Kirschenhofer, 1984, paratype (NHMW), 1.53 mm 7 B. (P.) lulinense Habu, 1973 (drawing from Habu 1973), 1.41 mm 8 Bembidion (Peryphus) psuchrum Andrewes, 1935, holotype (NHMUK), 0.91 mm 9 Bembidion (Plataphus) pseudolucillum Netolitzky, paratype (NHMW), 0.80 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1044.62593.figures5-9" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/555047" pageId="0" pageNumber="563">9</figureCitation>
) shows that the species belongs to subgenus 
<taxonomicName id="88C3F9C0EDC52EF5904FDE445C32CA55" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Bembidion (Plataphus)" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subGenus" subGenus="Plataphus">Bembidion Plataphus</taxonomicName>
Motschulsky, 1864. The doubts regarding the systematic position of the species are due to its pronotal convexity, more evident than in other species of the subgenus. We added to all the non-type specimens the following label: 
<taxonomicName id="5F2699ACEEE376408BB2D7DAA8C33A58" authorityName="Neri &amp; Toledano" authorityYear="2021" baseAuthorityName="Neri &amp; Toledano" baseAuthorityYear="1938" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Bembidion (Plataphus) pseudolucillum" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pseudolucillum" subGenus="Plataphus">Bembidion (Plataphus) pseudolucillum</taxonomicName>
Net. - det. Neri and Toledano 2020. The species length varies from 3.6 to 4.7 mm, the aedeagus from 0.75 to 0.84 mm.
</paragraph>
